MRI Infarcts: 2021-01-29

Source: R/data.R
MRI_INFARCTS.Rd

MRI Infarcts: 2021-01-29 data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(MRI_INFARCTS)

Format

A data frame with 8593 observations and 16 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3

  • COLPROT character Study protocol of data collection , with options: ADNI1, ADNI3, ADNI2, ADNIGO, nv

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 2, ..., 6795

  • VISCODE character Visit code ADNI code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • MRI.DATE2 Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • MRI.DATE1 Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • ANALYZE.DATE Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • SIDE character Side of Infarct, if detected R/L or -

  • SIZE character Size of Infarct, if detected Small/Large or -

  • CVA.NUMBER numeric Range value: 0, ..., 22

  • CVA.LOCATION character

  • CVA.TYPE character , with options: -, THROMBOSIS, HEMORRHAGE, UNANALYZABLE

  • XYZ character

  • IMGFILE character

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
